text: Niscaya muchalima purausa arau muchalima narai, mumina purausa arau mumina narai, anugata purausa arau anugata narai, satyabadi purausa arau satyabadi narai, dhairyasila purausa arau dhairyasila narai, binita purausa arau binita narai, danasila purausa arau danasila narai, cha'oma palanakarai purausa arau cha'oma palanakarai narai, yaunanga hiphajatakarai purausa arau yaunanga hiphajatakarai narai, allahaka adhika smaranakarai purausa arau allahaka adhika smaranakarai narai, te'omlokara babe allahe raakhiche ksama arau mahapratidana
